rows.label: qev091001_MSG0001
rows.name: Hmm. Guess I'm outta options...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0010
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask the man if he's all right.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0020
rows.name: Watch

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0021
rows.name: Hang back and say nothing.

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0002
rows.name: Heeeey! Are you thinking what I'm thinking?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0003
rows.name:
Wouldn't be here if you weren't, right? Perfect!
Let's drink—I'm buyin'![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0004
rows.name:
I don't want to drink alone,
but none of the others are free tonight...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0005
rows.name: Hmmm, maybe I could—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0006
rows.name: Heeeeey! It's the answer to my problems![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0007_m
rows.name:
Nice to meet you, stranger.
I'm buying drinks, and you're helping me drink 'em![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0007_f
rows.name:
Nice to meet you, stranger.
I'm buying drinks, and you're helping me drink 'em![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0030
rows.name: Join

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0031
rows.name: Agree to a drink.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0040
rows.name: Decline

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0041
rows.name: Turn down the offer.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0050
rows.name: Protest

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0051
rows.name: Claim that you're underage.

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0008
rows.name:
That's what I wanted to hear!
Let's keep this party goin' till dawn! Ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0009
rows.name:
What, too good to drink my booze?
Nobody likes a wet blanket![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0010
rows.name: Come on, live a little! Let's party the night away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0011
rows.name:
So what? Have juice! Or milk!
Or whatever you kids are drinking these days.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0012
rows.name: All I'm asking for is a little company while I tip a few back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0013
rows.name:
Oh man, good times. The best!
I didn't think we'd actually go till dawn![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0014_m
rows.name: Right then! You ready for the main event?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0014_f
rows.name: Right then! You ready for the main event?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0060
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0061
rows.name: Ask what's up next.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0070
rows.name: Suggest

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0071
rows.name: Say that perhaps he should get some sleep.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0080
rows.name: Rally

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0081
rows.name: Offer to buy the next round.

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0015
rows.name: You gotta ask?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0016
rows.name:
Crackin' indigen skulls, of course!
What else would an Interceptor do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0018
rows.name: Sleep? I'm on duty![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0019
rows.name: And those toothy critters ain't gonna fight themselves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0020
rows.name: ...What? You look surprised.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0021
rows.name: Haw haw! We got a live one here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0022
rows.name:
Sorry, buddy, but daylight hours are for working.
Time to get useful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0023
rows.name:
Hey, don't look so surprised.
I like to have fun, but I'm still a BLADE, ya know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0024
rows.name: Anyway, guess I never introduced myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0025
rows.name: The name's Frye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0026
rows.name: The rest of the Interceptors call me the Killer Ostrich.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0027
rows.name: ...Worst nickname ever, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0028
rows.name: Well, I love it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0029
rows.name:
I'm always taking the dangerous jobs
nobody else'll touch with a 10-foot pole.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0030
rows.name: Hence the nickname. Well, the "Killer" part, anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0031
rows.name: I take it as a compliment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0032
rows.name:
But it means I've gotta nix some nasties today
if I want to keep my rep.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0033
rows.name: Care to join me, seeing as we're old pals and all now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0090
rows.name: Accept

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0091
rows.name: Agree to help Frye with whatever he needs.

rows.label: qev091001_JNK0100
rows.name: Decline

rows.label: qev091001_SEL0101
rows.name: Say that you're busy.

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0034
rows.name: Hah! Good energy! I like you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0035
rows.name: Let's you and me knock this baby outta the park.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0036
rows.name: Aw, don't be like that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0037
rows.name: Come on, I'll protect you and everything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0039
rows.name: Today's mission is critter cleanup out in Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0042
rows.name: There's a lot of 'em, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0043
rows.name:
It'd be a hassle to explain it all,
so just check your comm device later, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091001_MSG0044
rows.name: We'll take 'em out in the order they're listed.[ST:wait ]
